name: Codename: Kids Next Door
overview: Taking numbers instead of names, five extraordinary 10-year-olds form a covert team called the Kids Next Door with one dedicated mission: to free all children from the tyrannical rule of adults.

episodes.name: Operation: C.A.K.E.D.
episodes.overview: The Kids Next Door attempt to stop a party for their enemies.

episodes.name: Diseasy Does It
episodes.overview: Kenny and Chimpy are hired to do chores.

episodes.name: No P in the OOL
episodes.overview: Mr. Wink and Mr. Fibb extend adult swim time.

episodes.name: Operation: I.-S.C.R.E.A.M.
episodes.overview: The Kids Next Door set off on a mission to the ice cream factory.

guest_stars.character: Ice Cream Man / Ice Cream Beast (voice)
guest_stars.name: Kevin Michael Richardson

episodes.name: Operation: C.A.N.N.O.N.
episodes.overview: With Numbuh One away, the Treehouse becomes an easy target for adults

episodes.name: Operation: N.O.-P.O.W.U.H.
episodes.overview: The hamsters that power the Treehouse go on vacation, leaving the team vulnerable.

episodes.name: Operation: T.E.E.T.H.
episodes.overview: The Kids Next Door are put in the crosshairs of Knightbraces.

episodes.name: Operation: P.I.R.A.T.E.
episodes.overview: Stickybeard and his crew sniff out the Kids Next Door's candy depository.

episodes.name: Operation: C.O.W.G.I.R.L.
episodes.overview: The team meets the last member of another era's Kids Next Door.

episodes.name: Operation: T.U.R.N.I.P.
episodes.overview: When turnips are found everywhere in Sector V's treehouse, they go to the source: a giant turnip, to defeat it.

episodes.name: Operation: M.I.N.I.G.O.L.F.
episodes.overview: After Numbuh 2 beats a mini-golf champion at mini-golf, the golfer shrinks Numbuh 2, and a whole lot of sights from around the world.

episodes.name: Operation: O.F.F.I.C.E.
episodes.overview: When his father brings Numbuh 4 to work for "Bring Your Daughter To Work Day", Numbuh 4 discovers his father's boss plans to send him and all the daughters of his coworkers to Pluto.

episodes.name: Operation: A.R.C.T.I.C.
episodes.overview: A fellow operative, Numbuh 30c, is sent to help Sector V stop a villain from using a weather machine to make no more snow days for school. It turns out that he was not helping, because he sent them the wrong directions, ignored their cries for help, and sent a missle to attack them.

episodes.name: Operation: L.I.C.E.
episodes.overview: The Delightful Children From Down The Lane attack Sector V's headquarters with an infestation of hair-eating lice. After the KND find out they don't like nacho cheese, they decide to shoot nacho cheese at them to get rid of them.

episodes.name: Operation: L.I.Z.Z.I.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 1 has a secret girlfriend who is bent on mind controling him! So, Numbuh 1's friends have to save Numbuh 1 from being mind controlled or their days as KND could be numbered.

episodes.name: Operation: T.H.E-F.L.Y.
episodes.overview: A fly finds its way into Sector V's headquarters.

episodes.name: Operation: P.O.I.N.T.
episodes.overview: All of the teenagers in Sector V's hometown have formed a place called The Point, and Numbuh 1 suspects that they are helping the adults.

episodes.name: Operation: C.A.B.L.E.-T.V.
episodes.overview: A villainous half-man, half-baby named Mr. B gives the Kids Next Door a television series of their own.

episodes.name: Operation: C.A.M.P.
episodes.overview: Can Numbuh 1 stop a camp counselor without the help of 2 and 3? Probably not...

episodes.name: Operation: T.O.M.M.Y.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 2's little brother, Tommy (who is shunned by Sector V) joins forces with a villain, Common Cold.

episodes.name: Operation: C.H.A.D.
episodes.overview: Two parental villains are stupefying KND operatives around the world; an operative named Chad (Numbuh 274) enlists the help of Sector V.

episodes.name: Operation: P.I.A.N.O.
episodes.overview: Sector V tries to destroy all the pianos in a truck with a hamster that acts as Numbuh 4's replacement.

episodes.name: Operation: Z.O.O.
episodes.overview: Sector V is put into a "kids zoo" and must unite with the Delightful Children From Down The Lane and get all the other children out of their cages before lunch time to escape being fed to the zoo's cannibal bully.

episodes.name: Operation: Q.U.I.E.T.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 5 tries to keep the treehouse quiet so Numbuh 1 can sleep.

episodes.name: Operation: R.A.I.N.B.O.W.S.
episodes.overview: The boss of Rainbow Monkeys Inc. uses Numbuh 3 to find real Rainbow Monkeys for him.

episodes.name: Operation: G.R.O.W.-U.P.
episodes.overview: The Delightful Children from Down the Lane turn to Father for help, and the Kids Next Door are forced into a dangerous showdown.

episodes.name: Operation: C.A.T.S.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 4 accidently destroys Numbuh 3's favorite toy, and then lands himself in the clutches of the creepy old cat lady and her billions of cats! Will his fellow operatives save him? And will Numbuh 3 forgive him in time TO save him?

episodes.name: Operation: P.O.P.
episodes.overview: When the drinking age of root beer is raised to 13, the Kids Next Door swing into action, delivering soda to speakeasies for youngsters. But soon the Kids discover the prohibtion's leader, Mr. Fizz, has something even more sinister in store. Can the Kids Next Door stop Fizz from bottling up children everywhere?

episodes.name: Operation: S.P.A.N.K.
episodes.overview: After spending a stretch in the slammer for spanking the wrong child, the vampiric villain Count Spankulot vows to use his abilities to help children instead of harm them, and approaches the Kids Next Door with an offer to join them! But when the former Bounty Hunter of Bottoms turns out to be more annoying now than he ever was as a villain, how will the KND get rid of the Pesky Paddler?

episodes.name: Operation: D.A.T.E.
episodes.overview: The Delightful Children From Down the Lane are holding a social, and the KND are invited! Smelling a rat, Numbah One and the team decide to go for a reconaissance mission - and as the only one without a date, he brings Lizzie along. But when the Delightful Children spring their trap, Lizzie becomes more of a hindrance than ever. Will Numbah 1 prevail? Will his relationship with Lizzie survive?!

episodes.name: Operation: S.U.P.P.O.R.T.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 5 is sick at home with the flu, and Numbuhs 1 and 2 take it upon themselves to protect her from the enemy. While at her house, her father lets it slip that teenage sister Cree is wearing a training bra! Ever suspisious of teenagers, Numbuh 1 figures that this odd device must be "Battle Ready Armor", and becomes determined to discover the workings behind it. But when the two of them are discovered, can even the Kids Next Door survive the wrath of a humiliated teenager?! And could there be more than meets the eye in this lingerie liason?

episodes.name: Operation T.A.P.I.O.C.A.
episodes.overview: On a seemingly routine mission, Numbuh 2 seizes a truckload of disgusting tapioca pudding from a trio of masked teenagers; unfortunatly, when trying to dispose of it, he plants it right in the middle of the treehouse! Now the team is up to their necks trying to clean up the putrid pudding, and the original teen-age owners still want it back! But why? Only Numbuh 2's grandmother knows for su

episodes.name: Operation: M.O.V.I.E.
episodes.overview: When Numbuh 4 is sickened by the cutsey "Rainbow Monkeys" double feature movie that the team goes to, he tries to theater-jump into to R-rated "Violence: The Movie," and after several unsuccessful tries, he makes it in disguised as an adult. But triumph turns to tragedy when he discovers that what promises to be a cool film is actually a front for a meeting for practically every villain that the KND have ever faced! And when his diguise fails, will Numbuh 4 escape this sinister cinema and leave room for a sequel?!

episodes.name: Operation F.A.S.T.-F.O.O.D.
episodes.overview: It's Numbuh 3's birthday! Her party seems to go well, until the team hears her birthday wish - to lead the team on a mission! Hoping to make her happy, Numbuh 1 quickly makes up a simple task for her - to retrieve a Kid's Meal from the new fast food place, the Burger Frenzy. But Numbuh 3 gets more than she bargains for when she discovers that, in this case, "Kid's Meal" actually refers to the main ingredient of the meal!

episodes.name: Operation: S.H.A.V.E.
episodes.overview: The KND learn about evil mustaches taking over the faces.

episodes.name: Operation: O.O.M.P-P.A.H.
episodes.overview: While on a fishing trip with his overbearing, sousaphone-playing father, Numbuh 1 has to rescue him from a kid seeking a father of his own.

episodes.name: Operation: F.L.A.V.O.R.
episodes.overview: Everbody knows that ice cream comes in three basic flavors - chocolate, vanilla, and strawberry. But Numbuh 5 knows only too well the legend of how the ancient ice cream monks created a FOURTH basic flavor, and hid it away in a hidden temple, where only an ice cream lover with the purest taste buds could ever taste it. But when the Delightful Children steal the sacred Golden Scoop, Numbuh 5 finds herself dragged to the trap-laden temple, where the evil children force her to penetrate its inner sanctum. Will Numbuh 5 prevail in this frozen frenzy and get a taste of the fabled Fourth Flavor?!

episodes.name: Operation: K.I.S.S.
episodes.overview: It is a clear case of Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde when Numbuh 2's attempt to create a formula to strengthen hamsters causes him to transform into a teenager and back! Thrown out of the treehouse by his unknowing teamates, he seemingly finds solace when he runs into Numbuh 5's evil sister Cree, and she develops a crush on him!

episodes.name: Operation: G.H.O.S.T.
episodes.overview: It is a sad day in the treehouse, when Chubbo, one of the KND's power-providing hamsters passes away; and it is saddest for the overly sensitive Numbuh 3, who even maintains a vigil at his grave until the weather proves inclement. But unwise is the one who mourns too long for the dead, because during the dark and stormy night, a gang of ghostly hamster arrive, and drag the terrified Three to the hamster afterlife! Now the team must penetrate the very netherworld to rescue their friend, but can even the KND overcome a mob of restless rodents?!

episodes.name: Operation F.U.G.I.T.I.V.E.
episodes.overview: An operative has apparently reached her thirteenth birthday, and is scheduled for decommission; but on route to the moon base, the transport ship carrying her is shanghied and forced to land. When the local KND arrive on the scene, they now must work with Decommission Officer Numbah 86, a boy-hating brat with a bad attitude! And when the fugitive flees to the Delightful Children's mansion, the

episodes.name: Operation: T.H.E.-S.H.O.G.U.N.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 2 and Numbuh 4 visit the grand opening of a cheese-themed restaurant which seems to have a big problem - an appalling lack of cheese! And when 2 reveals that he's brought his own, the source of the problem is revealed, when the operatives are kidnapped by cheese headed ninja, and then dragged before the Cheese Shogun, a mad martial artist who holds cheese to be more valueable than gold. Can 2 and 4 defeat this insane samurai and escape his deadly dairy dojo?!

episodes.name: Operation: C.O.L.L.E.G.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 1 hears word that a ten-year-old progidy has been accepted into a prestigious British College, and fears that the adults seek to remove his brain. With the rest of the team refusing to give up their day off, 1 travels across the Pond himself - only to find that the report was a ruse by the misunderstood mad scientist Professor Triple Extra-Large! The snow-cone expert has come close to perfecting his masterpiece, and now needs a test subject who is immune

episodes.name: Operation: R.E.P.O.R.T.
episodes.overview: The team is giving a report on their mission to retrieve a mysterious box, while trying to keep the Delightful Children from getting it. Unfortunately, each operative's version of the story is... exaggerated to say the least. Can their superiors find any truth in their speculative snafu?

episodes.name: Operation: B.R.I.E.F.
episodes.overview: The Delightful Children put out a contract on Numbah One's head, and send the most unlikely of assassins - the sentient pair of underpants known as Mr. White! Unfortunately, his attacks make the team think that their leader has gone loco! Can Numbah One survive the assault of this unruly underwear? And is there more to this pair of beastly briefs than meets the eye?

episodes.name: Operation: C.A.K.E.D.-T.W.O.
episodes.overview: The Delightful Children once again hold their annual birthday party in the usual sadistic manner planning to eat their cake and not let any of their unwilling guests have so much as a taste.

guest_stars.character: Fake Delightful Child from Down the Lane (voice)
guest_stars.name: Tom Kenny

episodes.name: Operation: S.P.A.C.E.
episodes.overview: On a rountine mission to the Moon Base - in which Numbuh 3 is forced to bring along her kid sister Moshi - the team encounters a seemingly abandoned prison transport ship; and thanks to Moshi, they crash into it.

episodes.name: Operation: B.E.A.C.H.
episodes.overview: The KND take a vacation to the beach (and Numbuh 1 promptly leaves, since he hates the place), where Numbuh 3 is quickly kidnapped by the armored Kinights of the Round Towel, who drag her before King Sandy, a miniature monarch who quickly falls in love with her! Naturally, the concerned Numbuhs 4 with Numbuhs 2 and 5 confronting the beachcombing brat in his enormous sandcastle... but they are soon overwhelmed. Can the KND topple this tiny tyrant before high tide?

episodes.name: Operation: U.N.D.E.R.C.O.V.E.R.
episodes.overview: The Delightful Children have the team right where they want them (again), when suddenly, the helmet headed member (his name revealed as Lenny) pushes the wrong button on their vehicle, ruining the villains' plans. The KND start to head home, when they are called to the Moon Base, where they meet with Numbuh 274... and Lenny himself! The Delightful Child claims that he is the reason that his siblings plans always fail, and that he intends to help the KND organization by

episodes.name: Operation: D.O.G.-F.I.G.H.T.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 2 has always been one of the best pilots in the organization but one day while taking his 2X4 aircraft for a spin, he's shot down by a mysterious child pilot with a 2X4 plane of his own. 2 seeks revenge, but the pilot is untouchable, and manages to shoot him down out of every aircraft in the team's arsenal. Considering giving up, piloting, finally finds a way to defeat the pilot only to discover that his supplier has been fooling them both into fighting each other in a plot to destroy every chili dog in town!

episodes.name: Operation T.R.I.P.
episodes.overview: Father learns that Numbuh 3 is traveling to her homeland to meet up with the secret Japanese branch of the Kids Next Door; so he sends his best spies, the Interesting Twins From Beneth the Mountain, to trail Kuki and find the location of the Japanese agents' hideaway so an attack can be made. But when the two young spies trail 3, a combination of thei

episodes.name: Operation: E.N.D.
episodes.overview: When Numbuh 1 is fishing with his dad, Numbuh 86 and her group appear and tell him that he's been scheduled for a decommissioning! Although he escapes, his teammates are taken to be decommissioned, so he has to enlist the help of Numbuh 2's little brother Tommy to try and save them! Unfortunatly, he is too late, but can he still save the Moon Base from a fiery demise?

episodes.name: Operation: F.U.T.U.R.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 4 learns he is to be sent to a boarding school but he isn't worried, as he's always escaped from them before. But then he learns that the school is being run by the evil child Madam Margie, a girl who is getting high-tech aid from none other than her future self! Madam Margie's abominable plan is to create a twisted utopia where girls rule the world, using a demonic weapon called the girlifying ray that can turn anything feminine! The team seeming doesn't stand a chance until they recieve aid from a strange source Numbuh 4's OWN future self!

episodes.name: Operation: A.F.L.O.A.T.
episodes.overview: The Team attempts to crash the Annual We Hate The Kids Next Door Barbecue, only to find that the party has far more villains than they can handle! The team flees in their M.E.G.A.R.A.G.E aircraft, but Stickbeard and his band of buccaneers do not give up pursuit! When their craft is shot down by the Sweet Revenge, they land in the worst of places - in the middle of the ocean, in a disgusting sargasso of asparagus! Stranded, lost, with no edible food, a bad situation gets much worse when they are found by a great white aspargus monster! And when the vile vegetable seeks to make them its prey, all hope seems lost. Can their be any escape from this savage sprout?!

episodes.name: Operation L.E.A.D.E.R.
episodes.overview: Nigel is exhausted and dirty after a hard mission, and when he takes a break, Lizzie intercepts a mission spec from Numbuh 65.3. Deciding to give Nigel a break, Lizzie tricks the rest of the team into thinking Nigel put him in charge, and assumes the role as leader. But Lizzie i

episodes.name: Operation: U.T.O.P.I.A.
episodes.overview: The evil Chester is developing his Happy Headband a strange device he plans to sell to parents to keep kids out of their hair.

episodes.name: Operation: R.O.B.B.E.R.S.
episodes.overview: It's time for the morning commute to school, and for once, Numbuh 4 is anxious to go, mostly because he has a crush on the new teacher. But on the way to school, the bus is attacked by kids dressed by cowboys packing chewing-gun loaded six-shooters, demanding the students' spelling homework! Now Numbuh 4 pursues the bandits outside, while Numbuh 5 engages them on the bus itself. Can they save the day before first bell? And who is the brains behind these delinquent desperadoes?!

episodes.name: Operation: F.O.U.N.T.A.I.N.
episodes.overview: The Delightful Children kidnap the team's classmate, nerdy, spit-talking ""Leaky"" Leona, and force her to lead them to the dark underbellies of the school. Alerted by Numbuh 5, the team follows them, and find themselves in an ancient school, laden with deadly booby traps. Avoiding them all, the team finds Leona, strangely aged to an old woman, who leads them to the mythical Fountain of Youth! The KND are amazed at the prospect of remaining ten years old forever, but the Delightful Children desire nothing less than to destroy the Fountain, claiming that the goal of all children should be to grow up. Can the Kids Next door save the supernatural spring? And what strange secret is ""Leaky"" Leona hiding?

episodes.name: Operation: B.U.T.T.
episodes.overview: Feeling that Numbuh 1 must take a day off, the team force him to go to the beach, telling him to have fun or else. Nigel makes an honest attempt - until a crab swipes his swim trunks! After suffering a great amount of public embarrassment, 1 makes his way back to the Treehouse... and minutes later, walks out of his room to tell his terrified team that he's resigning from the Kids Next Door! After he leaves, the purpose becomes quite clear... an envelope is found in his room from the Delightful Children, with a picture of his tush and a note saying ""Leave your team behind or we'll put your behind in the school yearbook."" Now Numbuh 1 is heading for Delightful Manor, where the evil peeping toms desire to make him one of them! Can the team save their leader from the sadistic shutterbugs?!

episodes.name: Operation: T.R.A.I.N.I.N.G.
episodes.overview: At the KND Arctic training facility (the second largest KND base in existence, and location of the top secret KND Code Module), young cadet Tommy is

episodes.name: Operation: A.R.C.H.I.V.E.
episodes.overview: The true history of the genesis of the Adult-Child conflict is revealed. This is the story the Adults do not want you to hear.

episodes.name: Operation: S.L.U.M.B.E.R.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 86 is having a top-secret girls only slumber party. Numbuh 4 is willing to find out what the slumber party is all about even if it means having to put on a little make up.

episodes.name: Operation: P.I.N.K.-E.Y.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 2 has set up a private eye office in the school janitor closet and soon he gets his first case someone is inflicting students with bad cases of pink-eye. When Numbuh 86 becomes the latest victim and he gets no help from Joe the hall monitor (his old partner before he joined the KND) 2 does some of his own deductive work until Joe attacks him.

guest_stars.character: Numbuh 86 / Nurse Claiborne / Rainbow Monkey Chorus (voice)
guest_stars.name: Jennifer Hale

episodes.name: Operation: K.A.S.T.L.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 3 takes her little sister Mushi for a ride through the Rainbow Monkey Sugar Coated Castle of Love, but what promises to be a day of fun is ruined when King Sandy and his knights attack! The insane sovereign has never given up in his quest to marry Numbuh 3, and he threatens to destroy the Rainbow Monkeys unless Kuki agre

episodes.name: Operation: C.A.K.E.D.-T.H.R.E.E.
episodes.overview: It's the Delightful Children From Down The Lane's birthday again, and that means it's time once again for the Kids Next Door to make off with their fantastic cake! But when the plan to egg the Delightfuls to submission goes afowl, the Kids must decide whether the cake is really worth it.

episodes.name: Operation: L.O.C.K.D.O.W.N.
episodes.overview: Upon returning to the Treehouse, an injured Numbuh 1 orders a lockdown! But it soon becomes clear that the five are trapped with Count Spankulot! But is the Count the real intruder? Or is another spank-happy vampire in their midsts?

episodes.name: Operation: G.R.A.D.U.A.T.E.S
episodes.overview: Hoagie and the gang go to the KND Academy to watch his brother Tommy graduate while Father plans an all-out attack.

episodes.name: Operation: H.U.G.S.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 4's disgust at anything Rainbow Monkey only increases when he finds himself trapped on Rainbow Island.

episodes.name: Operation: J.E.W.E.L.S.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 5 journeys to the exotic Al-Suhgar Desert to recover her stolen candy, the Blurpleberry Supreme, and discovers she's not the only one searching for the powerful, mystical candy.

episodes.name: Operation: T.R.I.C.K.Y.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 4 tries to get his candy back from Stickybeard on Halloween.

episodes.name: Operation: P.R.E.S.I.D.E.N.T.
episodes.overview: The KND try to get the Fourth Grade Class President to his Town Council meetings safely. A parody of Air Force One. Hurt Operative Safely Protected In Totally Antiseptic Location

episodes.name: Operation: H.O.S.P.I.T.A.L.
episodes.overview: An important operative suffers an accident on a dangerous mission and is sent to the hospital. But one ex-KND member is out to scramblify his brain, and it's up to Sector V to make sure he is safe, especially Numbuh 3.

episodes.name: Operation: S.P.R.O.U.T.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 4 accidentally eats a brussels sprout, sending the rest of the KND on an emergency Fantastic Voyage to stop the dreaded vegetable from being digested.

episodes.name: Operation: H.O.U.N.D.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 5 takes on a vicious dog who is always eating her homework.

episodes.name: Operation R.A.B.B.I.T.
episodes.overview: Numbuhs 2 and 5 must rescue the first grade class's pet rabbit before it is turned into a chocolate bunny by Heinrich Von Marzipan.

episodes.name: Operation: FLUSH
episodes.overview: The villains attempt to capture the KND Treehouse, but the Toilenator, trying to be helpful, only hinders their plans.

episodes.name: Operation F.O.O.D.F.I.T.E.
episodes.overview: The KND are dismayed to discover that Grandma Stuffum is the new cafeteria lunch lady and she's got some pretty nasty recipes to foist on her pint-sized nemeses.

episodes.name: Operation: C.L.U.E.S.
episodes.overview: A dinner get-together between Numbuh 2 and Numbuh 3's respective families turns sour when Numbuh 3's Posh Party Rainbow Monkey doll is badly damaged with a fork in its back. Now it's up to Numbuh 2 to figure out the murderer of the doll.

episodes.name: Operation N.U.G.G.E.T.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 4 discovers a chicken nugget that initiates a chicken nugget rush.

episodes.name: Operation: M.A.C.A.R.R.O.N.I.
episodes.overview: The Kids Next Door have the misfortune of swapping the Toilenator to Mr. Boss with the unlucky Numbuh 13, who informs the operatives of the adult villains' plans for a macaroni dinner by ransacking a museum of macaroni art.

episodes.name: Operation P.O.O.L.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 4's newly-installed backyard pool is the portal into an alternate dimension where everything is the opposite of everything in the real world.

episodes.name: Operation C.A.K.E.D.-F.O.U.R.
episodes.overview: The Delightful Children From Down the Lane decide to give their birthday cake to the winner of the annual Tubathon race and everyone is eager to go for it. No one is more eager than Numbuh 2, who plans to use his old tube, Betsy, and "farfegtubing". But are the Delightfuls keeping their word about the cake or are they luring the competitors into a trap?

episodes.name: Operation S.I.T.T.E.R.
episodes.overview: The brothers Gilligan have gotten a new babysitter: the villainous Cree Lincoln! For Numbuh 2, this will either be a dream come true or a nightmare.

episodes.name: Operation: S.A.T.U.R.N.
episodes.overview: Everyone's collections of Rainbow Monkey toys are mysteriously vanishing. The KND investigate and discover the toys revolving around the planet Saturn as its big ring!

episodes.name: Operation: C.H.O.C.O.L.A.T.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 5 goes to the planet Mars to pick up some marshmallows as part of dessert with her family after dinner. But upon her return, she discovers her family and friends are being menaced by an old foe who now is a mere shell of his old self.

episodes.name: Operation: M.A.T.A.D.O.R.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 4 is forced to choose between helping the KND battle the villainous Soccer Mom or engaging at his new gig as a matador in the Bully Fights.

episodes.name: Operation L.U.N.C.H.
episodes.overview: Lizzie had made a romantic lunch for both her and "Nigie", but it gets stolen by Robin Food and his Hungry Men, who rob from the young and give to the old.

episodes.name: Operation: M.U.N.C.H.I.E.S.
episodes.overview: The KND discover that they're out of Rainbow Munchies cereal, so they try to go to a grocery store to get some more. But the only grocery store that sells such a product is the villains-only store called the Super-Villains Supermarket & Deli.

episodes.name: Operation K.N.O.T.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 1, both literally and figuratively, risks his neck when he sides with an adult to rid children of snake-like ties.

episodes.name: Operation: C.L.O.S.E.T.
episodes.overview: A boy gets lost in a closet and the KND are on the job in no time.

episodes.name: Operation S.N.O.W.I.N.G.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 1 is sick in bed with a cold on a snow day. Even worse, the villainous Fourth Grade President is determined to bring the children, who are all taking advantage of the snow day, to school for a special assembly.

episodes.name: Operation M.A.U.R.I.C.E.
episodes.overview: An operate named Maurice is decommissioned from the Kids Next Door after he attains the age of 13. He has been working on a cure for chicken pox. The one who is saddened the most by his departure is Numbuh 5, so she suggests that they keep an eye on him so that the teenagers don't recruit him.

episodes.name: Operation L.O.V.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 3 stars as the lead female in a "West Side Story"-style romantic musical. But when Numbuh 4 interrupts the play, the war that follows between the Kids Next Door and the Delightful Children From Down the Lane is anything but staged.

episodes.name: Operation: C.O.U.C.H.
episodes.overview: Numbuhs 1, 2 and 5 all go off to China after Numbuh 4 falsely alerts them of trouble there. He then watches TV in their absence, but Numbuh 3 doesn't leave, either, and they fight over the remote control, which falls into the couch. Numbuh 4 goes into the couch after it... and winds up a strange world where everyone is named Dave, who want the control for themselves.

episodes.name: Operation D.O.D.G.E.B.A.L.L.
episodes.overview: The powerful Dodgeball Wizard believes that adults are better at playing dodgeball than kids, so when he learns of "the one called Beetles," a kid who is a greater dodgeball player than he is, he becomes determined to destroy his rival. And that rival is, apparently, Numbuh 4!

episodes.name: Operation: F.E.R.A.L.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 1 is sent to retrieve an important code from Rainbow Monkey Island, but after a run-in with the Delightful Children From Down the Lane, he is left stranded there. Soon, he ends up forgetting who he is and starts behaving like a wild Rainbow Monkey. His teammates become very worried when it appears that there may be no way to cure him.

episodes.name: Operation N.A.U.G.H.T.Y.
episodes.overview: A Christmas Episode.

episodes.name: Operation: L.I.C.O.R.I.C.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 5 must team up with Stickybeard to save Heinrich Von Marzipan from a crew of skeletal licorice pirates.

episodes.name: Operation H.O.M.E.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 3 has second thoughts about sending her old Rainbow Monkey to a retirement home.

episodes.name: Operation: I.T.
episodes.overview: Numbuh 362 becomes frustrated with all the work involved with being Supreme Leader of the Kids Next Door, so she decides to give up her position. But everything goes horribly wrong when Father takes her place!
